🎮 Gaming Tournament Website

A modern and responsive Gaming Tournament Website built using HTML and CSS.
This project provides a platform for gamers to explore tournaments, view rules, and compete for exciting rewards.

---

🚀 Features

- 🎯 Interactive and responsive design
- 🕹️ Tournament information section
- 📜 Rules and guidelines for fair play
- ⚖️ Terms & Conditions section
- 🏆 Winning prizes display
- 💡 Clean UI with modern gaming theme
- ✨ Hover effects and animations

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Visual Studio Code

---


🎯 Purpose of the Project

The main goal of this project is to practice and demonstrate frontend development skills by creating a visually appealing and responsive gaming website.

